      "body": "\n<p>\n            W obu trójkątach na rysunku poniżej jeden z boków ma długość 1.\n        </p>\n<p>\n<img alt=\"kąty 30, 45, 60 - pytanie\" height=\"579\" src=\"static/tryg_30_45_60.png\" style=\"width: 799px; height: 579px;\" width=\"799\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n            Jakie są długości boków oznaczonych literami \\(a\\), \\(b\\), \\(c\\) i \\(d\\)?\n        </p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<ul>\n<li>\n<div class=\"statement\" data-width=\"150px\">\n                Długość \\(a\\) to:\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(1\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{2}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{3}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(2\\)\n            </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"statement\" data-width=\"150px\">\n                Długość \\(b\\) to:\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(1\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{2}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{3}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(2\\)\n            </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"statement\" data-width=\"150px\">\n                Długość \\(c\\) to:\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(1\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{2}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{3}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(2\\)\n            </div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"statement\" data-width=\"150px\">\n                Długość \\(d\\) to:\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(1\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{2}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(\\sqrt{3}\\)\n            </div>\n<div class=\"one_choice ks_button\">\n                \\(2\\)\n            </div>\n</li>\n</ul>"
